        "comment": {
            "name": "comment",
            "type": "com.atlassian.jira.issue.fields.CommentSystemField",
            "value": [
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/28228",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "To turn off escaping, pass the 'escape' key to the $attribs argument:\n\n{code}\n$this->formLabel('foo', '<b>Label!<\/b>', array('escape' => false));\n{code}\n\nLine 54 of the helper class reads as follows:\n{code}\n$value = ($escape) ? $this->view->escape($value) : $value;\n{code}\n\nBy default, if no escape key is passed, then it is set to true; if you pass a value evaluating as false, it will not escape the value. There are tests for this functionality, and I have just verified it myself.\n",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2009-01-15T04:31:53.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2009-01-15T04:31:53.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/28232",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=jitka_sunny",
                        "name": "jitka_sunny",
                        "displayName": "Ing. Jitka Darbujanova",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "ok, and what if it is label of some element. This code doesn't work:\n\n$myEl = new Zend_Form_Element_Text('myEl');\n$myEl ->setLabel('text <span class=\"label_help\">(for auto text, leave it empty)<\/span>:');\n$myEl ->setAttrib('escape' , false);",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=jitka_sunny",
                        "name": "jitka_sunny",
                        "displayName": "Ing. Jitka Darbujanova",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2009-01-15T05:48:17.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2009-01-15T05:48:17.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/28235",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "In that case, you set it on the decorator:\n{code}\n$myEl->getDecorator('label')->setOption('escape', false);\n{code}\n\nor, at element instantiation:\n{code}\n$myEl = new Zend_Form_Element_Text('myEl', array(\n    'label' => 'text<span class=\"label_help\">(for auto text, leave it empty)<\/span>:',\n    'decorators' => array(\n        'ViewHelper',\n        'Errors',\n        'Description',\n        array('HtmlTag', array('tag' => 'dd')),\n        array('Label', array('escape' => false, 'tag' => 'dt')),\n    ),\n));\n{code}\n\nPlease ask questions like these on the mailing lists prior to posting issues in the future.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2009-01-15T06:21:59.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2009-01-15T06:21:59.000+0000"
                },
